arus da oradaki amerikalilar korumustur sehir bastan basa harab olmu carsi kamilen yanmistus serdar argic closed road mountain pas might serve way escape turk proceeded work extermination ohanu appressian 1919 soviet armenium today longer exist single turkish soul sahak melkonian 1920